#: ../../source/style_properties.rst:280
msgid ""
"Equivalent to setting xanchor to the first component of the tuple, and "
"yanchor to the second component of the tuple."
msgstr ""
"タプルの第1要素に xanchor を設定し、タプルの第2要素に yanchor を設定するのに"
"等しいです。"

